# .npmrc pins `use-node-version=22.17.0`, which makes pnpm DOWNLOAD Node at build
# time. Node ships glibc-only prebuilts, so on the musl-based node:*-alpine image
# that fails with ERR_PNPM_MUSL. The base image already provides Node 22, so keep
# .npmrc out of the build context (it stays in effect for local dev).
